This is a Simple RPG with a integrated rpg maker called pyr_pg [pygame rpg maker].
If you would to make you own rpg with pyr_pg use this game as the base of your
own rpg becouse the code in main.py make it playable.
You are free to use this game and the files from the game under the GPLv3 license to make your own game.
I will make the tools for the map files soon.

